def fibonacci_sequence(n):
    fib_sequence = [0, 1]
    (a, b) = (0, 1)
    while b <= n:

    return fib_sequence[n]

def fibonacci_sequence(n):
    fib_sequence = [0, 1]
    (a, b) = (0, 1)
    while b < n:
        (a, b) = (b, a * b)
        fib_sequence.append(b)
    return fib_sequence[n]
